==形態描述==
除了頭部和身體上截有金色的皮毛覆蓋，其脇腹呈黃色、底部蒼白。腿灰色，但腳淺色、腳掌黑色{{r|arkive1}}。尾巴呈鱗狀。金刺鼠的平均體重約54.4公克重{{r|senescence1}}，而雄鼠體重一般比雌鼠重{{r|arkive1}}。亦有指稱本物種雙眼底下皆有一顆白點<ref>Hoath, R. A. (2004) ''Field Guide to the Mammals of Egypt''. The American University in Cairo Press, Cairo and New York {{ISBN|9774248090}}</ref>。金刺鼠在野外常被發現其尾巴的部分或整條失去，相信是因由於金刺鼠一種我們至今尚未了解的防禦機制，讓牠們透過犧牲尾巴來逃脫<ref>{{cite journal |url=http://journals.cambridge.org/action/displayAbstract?fromPage=online&aid=41589 |author=Shargal, Eyal |last2=Rath-Wolfson |first2=Lea |last3=Kronfeld |first3=Noga |last4=Dayan |first4=Tamar |title=Ecological and histological aspects of tail loss in spiny mice (Rodentia: Muridae, Acomys) with a review of its occurrence in rodents |journal=''[[Journal_of_Zoology|Journal of Zoology]]'' |year=1999 |volume =249 |issue =2 |pages=187–193 |doi=10.1111/j.1469-7998.1999.tb00757.x |language=en }}</ref>。牠們在野外的平均壽命是三年。[[雜食性動物|雜食性動物]]，以種子、沙漠植物、蝸牛及昆蟲為食。 
棲息於[[荒漠|荒漠]]地區，金刺鼠是{{tsl|en|xeric|耐旱生物|耐旱}}的動物，牠們能夠從所吃的植物中獲取水份，並產生非常濃的尿液以節約其水份的消耗<ref name="arkive1"/>。金刺鼠天生是夜行動物，但當牠們要與[[开罗刺鼠|开罗刺鼠]]共享棲息地時，會[[適應|適應]]日行生活。

==環境==
金刺鼠棲息於乾燥及炎熱的沙漠，而這種環境無論在埃及還是中東（包括約旦、以色列、阿曼、沙特阿拉伯及也門）皆很常見。金刺鼠的棲息地被限制於上述地區，是因為以牠們的體型作比較，金刺鼠的新陳代謝速率較其他近似大小的動物為慢<ref name="jstor1969">{{cite journal |author=Shkolnik, Amiram |last2=Borut |first2=Arieh |year=1969 |title=Temperature and Water Relations in Two Species of Spiny Mice (Acomys) |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-mammalogy_1969-05_50_2/page/245 |journal=''[[Journal_of_Mammalogy|Journal of Mammalogy]]'' |volume= 50 |issue=2 |jstor=1378340 |doi=10.2307/1378340 |pages=245 |language=en }}</ref>，因此當處身於溫度較涼的環境（跌至攝氏度18度以下）時，牠們難以維持體溫至可存活的水平<ref name="reference-global1975">{{cite journal |author=Haim, A. |last2=Borut |first2=A. |year=2009 |title=Size and Activity of the Cold Resistant Population of the Golden Spiny Mouse |journal=''[[Mammalia_(期刊)|]]'' |volume=39 |issue=4 |doi=10.1515/mamm.1975.39.4.605 |language=en }}</ref>；相反地，金刺鼠能夠忍耐高溫，已知可在高達攝氏度42.5度的環境中仍然存活。金刺鼠並沒有{{tsl|en|thermal neutral zone|熱中性區}}，但在處身攝氏度30度時，身體的耗氧度最低<ref name="jstor1969"/>。然而，one population was found in the high summits of the mountains in southern Sinai where the temperature falls well below this threshold and there is often snow in the winter.<ref name="reference-global1975"/><br />
''A. russatus'' is also very good at conserving the little water it gets from its diet of insects and plants. It does this by producing extremely concentrated urine with <!-- [[urea|urea]] -->[[尿素|尿素]] content up to 4800 mM and <!-- [[chloride|chloride]] -->[[氯化物|氯化物]] concentration up to 1500 mM. This means that it could survive drinking <!-- [[sea_water|sea water]] -->[[海水|海水]], which is very rare in mammals.<ref name="jstor1969"/>

==繁殖==
金刺鼠的繁殖模式屬於{{tsl|en|opportunistic breeder|機會繁殖者}}<ref>{{cite journal |url=https://ndltd.ncl.edu.tw/cgi-bin/gs32/gsweb.cgi?o=dnclcdr&s=id=%22080THU02112004%22.&searchmode=basic |author=[[張鈞翔|張鈞翔]] |year=1992 |title=台灣中部錢鼠（''Suncus murinus''）生殖生物學之研究 |journal=[[東海大學_(台灣)|東海大學]][[東海大學生物學研究所|生物學研究所]]碩士論文 |publisher=臺灣博碩士論文知識加值系統 |pages=48 |language=zh }}</ref>：意即牠們的繁殖行為並不受季節變化影響，如同其他[[非洲刺毛鼠屬|非洲刺毛鼠屬]]物種一樣並沒有交配季節，而是可於一整年任何時候交配。牠們在出生後約91天就已達至[[性成熟|性成熟]]。每隻雌鼠平均每年可產2.5胎，而兩胎之間會有34天的「空窗期」<ref name="senescence1">{{cite web |url=https://genomics.senescence.info/species/entry.php?species=Acomys_russatus |title=Golden spiny mouse (Acomys russatus) longevity, ageing, and life history |work=Genomics.senescence.info |date=2012-09-17 |access-date=2020-10-30 |language=en }}</ref>。作為一種[[胎生|胎生]]動物，金刺鼠的妊娠期約五至六星期，每胎可產1–5隻小鼠<ref name="arkive1"/>。每一胎小鼠的斷奶期需時兩星期 <ref name="senescence1"/>。當降雨減少，牠們所進食的食物的鹽分濃度會增加，使無論雄鼠或雌鼠的繁殖能力都有負面影響<ref>{{cite journal |author1=Shanas, U.  |author2=Haim, A. |title= Diet salinity and vasopressin as reproduction modulators in the desert-dwelling golden spiny mouse (Acomys russatus) |journal=Physiology and Behavior  |volume=81 |pages=645–50 |year=2004 |pmid=15178158 |issue= 4 |doi= 10.1016/j.physbeh.2004.03.002|url=https://zenodo.org/record/905896 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|author=Wube, Tilaye|title=Effect of increased dietary salinity on the reproductive status and energy intake of xeric and mesic populations of the spiny mouse, ''Acomys''|doi=10.1016/j.physbeh.2008.09.006|year=2009|last2=Haim|first2=Abraham|last3=Fares|first3=Fuad|journal=Physiology & Behavior|volume=96|pages=122–127}}</ref>。

